  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Reflection</h2>
    <p>
      Enhancing SYLTrack reinforced the importance of building a strong foundation before focusing on visual polish. I learned that
      navigation consistency and clean architecture have a major impact on the usability and maintainability of an application.
      One challenge was balancing improvements to user flow with keeping the code organized and scalable. Overall, this enhancement
      strengthened my ability to revise an existing software solution with professional standards in mind.
    </p>
  </div>

